DefaultReaderConfiguration.fullDescription: Collects events from Nortel Baystack switches.

file.toolTipText: Directory or path to read from

string.toolTipText: Hostname of the nDepth appliance to receive log data

integer.toolTipText: Port number of the nDepth appliance to receive log data

select.toolTipText: Data routing (normalized alerts to Manager and/or raw data to nDepth)

integer.toolTipText: Number of seconds between log reads

FastPattern.pattern: ^\d+ [-\w.]+.* IGMP configuration failed. Loaded to factory default

FastPattern.matcher: ^(\d+) ([-\w.]+).* (IGMP new Querier IP [-\w.]+ learned on port (\d+))
FastPattern.pattern: ^\d+ [-\w.]+.* IGMP new Querier IP [-\w.]+ learned on port \d+
^\d+ [-\w.]+.* IGMP exchange database sent by unit \d+
^\d+ [-\w.]+.* IGMP exchange database received on unit \d+ from \d+

FastPattern.description: 12, RoutingTrafficAudit: IGMP not able to join stack
FastPattern.pattern: ^\d+ [-\w.]+.* IGMP not able to join stack: Error code \d+

FastPattern.description: 13, RoutingTrafficAudit: IGMP exchange group database sent
FastPattern.pattern: ^\d+ [-\w.]+.* IGMP exchange group database sent by unit \d+

FastPattern.description: 14, RoutingTrafficAudit: IGMP exchange group database received
FastPattern.pattern: ^\d+ [-\w.]+.* IGMP exchange group database received on unit \d+ from \d+

FastPattern.matcher: ^(\d+) ([-\w.]+).* (IGMP received \w+ on VLAN \d+ for Group \w+ on port (\d+)).*
FastPattern.pattern: ^\d+ [-\w.]+.* IGMP received (?:report|leave|query) on VLAN \d+ for Group \w+ on port \d+

FastPattern.description: 16, RoutingTrafficAudit: IGMP dynamic router port added/removed
